# Platform-aware hermesc binaries are downloaded at postinstall time
# (see ../src/hermesc-runtime.js). The two macOS prebuilts under
# darwin-arm64/ and darwin-x64/ are tracked (redundant offline
# fallback for Mac devs); everything else is pulled from the
# react-native npm tarball per platform at install time.

# Non-macOS platform subdirs — populated at install time.
linux-*/
win32-*/

# Legacy flat layout — never commit the stale top-level binary back.
/hermesc
/hermesc.exe
